* AgenticNativePlatform - Current GitOps Staging And Profile Composition
** 1. Source and generation flow
*** Operator
**** edits manifests and charts in repository source of truth
***** flux/components/*
***** charts/*
***** flux/overlays/*
**** commits and pushes to remote Git repository
***** GIT_REPO_URL @ GIT_BRANCH
*** Generated inputs
**** flux/generated/<topology>/
**** flux/generated/clusters/<cluster-id>/
**** produced by
***** make flux-values
***** make render-cluster-root
*** Effective flow
**** Repository source of truth -> Generated inputs -> Remote Git repository

** 2. Flux system reconciliation
*** GitRepository/platform
**** Flux reads the remote branch
**** Flux reconciles remote repository state, not local working tree
**** Generated manifests must be committed and pushed
*** platform-bootstrap
**** bootstrap content
***** base namespaces
***** Gateway API CRDs
***** Helm/OCI sources
***** generated ConfigMaps
***** secret references
**** staged dependency to platform-infrastructure
**** bootstrap-flux is rendered under flux/generated/clusters/<cluster-id>/bootstrap-flux/
**** the shell wrapper only applies that path
*** platform-infrastructure
**** selects infrastructure profile path
**** selects runtime overlay
***** none
***** ollama
***** vllm
**** staged dependency to platform-applications
**** optional dependency to platform-ops-ui
*** platform-applications
**** applies profile applications + env overlay
**** may render MetalLB values for host-based paths
**** optional dependency to platform-samples
*** Optional child roots
**** platform-ops-ui
***** suspend=true until enabled
***** deploys weave-gitops bundle
**** platform-samples
***** suspend=true until enabled
***** deploys samples-echo-mcp bundle

** 3. Profiles
*** platform-profile-full
**** base
**** network
**** agent-runtime
**** serving
**** context
**** observability
**** metallb
**** host-based default
*** platform-profile-fast
**** base
**** network
**** agent-runtime
**** metallb
**** explicit override
*** platform-profile-fast-serving
**** platform-profile-fast + serving
**** explicit override
*** platform-profile-fast-context
**** platform-profile-fast + context
**** explicit override
*** platform-profile-workspace
**** currently aliases platform-profile-fast-serving
**** github-workspace default

** 4. Bundle mapping
*** Applications profile
**** platform-apps
*** platform-profile-full -> bundles
**** platform-base
**** platform-network
**** platform-agent-runtime
**** platform-serving
**** platform-context
**** platform-observability
*** platform-profile-fast -> bundles
**** platform-base
**** platform-network
**** platform-agent-runtime
*** platform-profile-fast-serving -> bundles
**** inherits platform-profile-fast
**** platform-serving
*** platform-profile-fast-context -> bundles
**** inherits platform-profile-fast
**** platform-context
*** platform-profile-workspace -> bundles
**** aliases platform-profile-fast-serving
*** Optional bundles
**** weave-gitops bundle -> platform-ops-ui
**** samples-echo-mcp bundle -> platform-samples
